tc. Served TCS, Samsung, Engineers India Ltd, Technip Energies, Jacobs Engineering, Bechtel, KBR, & PSU’s in oil & gas, EPC sector for end to end recruitment. Maintain relationships with candidates to get references and spread networking. Handle joining & post joining life cycle of employees empaneled and Employee Exit Management Report generation. Knowledge of Payroll (PF, ESIC and Salary Breakups, Gratuity, Bonus, LWF). Completed two months Summer Internship in HR (recruitment and training process) from Tech Mahindra 1st June to 31stJuly 2020."}]'::jsonb, '[]'::jsonb, '[]'::jsonb, 'F:\Resume All 1\Resume PDF\Ashutosh Shukla Updated 2024.pdf', 'Name: Academic Credential

